---

<section class="portfolio-summary" aria-label="Portfolio overview">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="summary-content">
      <h2>Overview</h2>
      <p>
        M&A services span both the buy-side and sell-side executing technical diligence, preparing
        portfolio companies for sale and investment, and executing post-acquisition value creation
        initiatives to build value, reduce risks and costs while accelerating business objectives
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .portfolio-summary {
    padding: 3rem 0;
    background: transparent;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  .summary-content {
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  .portfolio-summary h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-family: monospace;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .portfolio-summary p {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-family: monospace;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .portfolio-summary {
      padding: 2rem 0;
    }

    .portfolio-summary h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .portfolio-summary p {
      font-size: var(--text-base);
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .portfolio-summary {
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }

    .portfolio-summary h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-xl);
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .portfolio-summary p {
      font-size: var(--text-sm);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
  }
</style>
